import React from 'react'
import { Container } from '../../GlobalStyles'
import { SignInForm, Title, Input, ConnectButton, InputWrapper, IconContainer, FormsWrapper } from './SignInSignUp.elements'
import {FaUserAlt} from 'react-icons/fa'
import {BsLockFill} from 'react-icons/bs'

const SignIn = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <FormsWrapper>
        <SignInForm>
          <Title>Se connecter</Title>
          <InputWrapper>
              <IconContainer>
                  <FaUserAlt style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
              </IconContainer>
              <Input placeholder='Email' type='email'/>
          </InputWrapper>
          <InputWrapper>
              <IconContainer>
                  <BsLockFill style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
              </IconContainer>
              <Input placeholder='Mot de passe' type='password'/>
          </InputWrapper>
          <ConnectButton>Se connecter</ConnectButton>
        </SignInForm>
        <SignInForm>
          <Title>Se connecter</Title>
          <InputWrapper>
              <IconContainer>
                  <FaUserAlt style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
              </IconContainer>
              <Input placeholder='Email' type='email'/>
          </InputWrapper>
          <InputWrapper>
              <IconContainer>
                  <BsLockFill style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
              </IconContainer>
              <Input placeholder='Mot de passe' type='password'/>
          </InputWrapper>
          <ConnectButton>Se connecter</ConnectButton>        
        </SignInForm>
      </FormsWrapper>
    </Container>
    </>
  )
}

export default SignIn
